# Sonde API Tests - TrenchAPI
@host = http://localhost:5127
@apiKey = ichliebetrench
@baseUrl = {{host}}

### Get All Sonden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Sonde
KEY: {{apiKey}}

### Get Sonde by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Sonde/1
KEY: {{apiKey}}

### Create New Sonde
# @name createSonde
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Sonde
KEY: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sondenTypID": 1,
  "name": "Test Sonde",
  "kalibrierungsfaktor": 1.5
}

### Update Sonde
@sondeId = 1
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Sonde/{{sondeId}}
KEY: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{sondeId}},
  "sondenTypID": 1,
  "name": "Updated Sonde",
  "kalibrierungsfaktor": 2.0
}

### Delete Sonde by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Sonde/999
KEY: {{apiKey}}

### Delete All Sonden
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Sonde
# KEY: {{apiKey}}
